==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unhelmed
<hw>Un*helmed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>unhelm</ets>.]</ety> <def>Divested or
deprived of the helm or helmet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>helm</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Not wearing a helmet; without a helmet.</def> <rj><au>Sir W.
Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unhelmet</ent>⟦br⟧
